description: Try our easy to follow Crisp Coconut Fish recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Crisp Coconut Fish Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Fill a large saucepan with vegetable oil to twothirds full. Heat over medium-high heat. To test if oil is hot enough, add a small piece of bread to oil. Don't overcrowd the pan. Cook 3-4 pieces at a time. Remove cooked pieces using a slotted spoon and drain on a wire rack over paper towel. Serve with wedges of lime and chips.
